%% Simulation Step Sequence - Compact
sequenceDiagram
    participant Orch as Orchestrator
    participant Sim as Simulation
    participant EB as EventBus
    participant Rules as RuleManager
    participant GUI as GUI

    Orch->>Sim: step()
    Sim->>Sim: read HDF5 data
    Sim->>EB: publish(GridDataEvent)
    EB->>Rules: evaluate()

    alt Rule triggered
        Rules->>EB: publish(RuleTriggeredEvent)
    end

    Sim->>EB: publish(SimulationStepEvent)
    EB->>Orch: handle events
    Orch->>GUI: update state
